                     <interp inst="t17930529-97-person1124" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , of Fenchurch-street, hatter and hosier, that was all he said; they were entered to him, Mr. 
               <persName id="t17930529-97-person1125">
                  Matthew
                   Gibbs
               <interp inst="t17930529-97-person1125" type="surname" value="Gibbs"></interp>
