                     <interp inst="t17930529-97-person1125" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was a customer of ours, and had been for many years; after he had looked them out they were tied up, I asked him his name? he said his name was Smith; I never knew that he was the son of 
               <persName id="t17930529-97-person1126">
                  Matthew
                   Gibbs
               <interp inst="t17930529-97-person1126" type="surname" value="Gibbs"></interp>
